"""
nex_belief_pyramid.py — Synthesis Pyramid for NEX
====================================================
Depth-stacked belief synthesis. Beliefs earn depth levels:

  depth=0  raw scraped/extracted beliefs (existing)
  depth=1  single-topic forge synthesis (existing synthesize_topic)
  depth=2  cross-topic synthesis — 2-3 topics collided together
  depth=3  meta-synthesis — depth=2 beliefs synthesized against each other
  depth=4+ reserved for future autonomous reasoning chains

Compounding logic:
  - depth=1 runs every 2h (existing forge cycle)
  - depth=2 runs every 4h (needs depth=1 inputs)
  - depth=3 runs every 8h (needs depth=2 inputs)
  Each depth layer is exponentially rarer and higher-value.

Wiring: import and call PyramidEngine().tick(current_cycle) from run.py
alongside BeliefForge.

Author: built for NEX v6.5+
"""

